Class GameObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • gameobjects.GameObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Building, Chest, Door, Fence, Item, NPC, Player, Tree, Wall

    public abstract class GameObject
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract class that holds all the information for GameObjects, these are objects such as Doors, Wall and Fences. This class holds the filename and the description of the object
